     <p align = "justify"> <span class = "content">
     <FONT COLOR="#FF6600"> <b>  Example 1.4 :   </b> </font> 

  Write an MPI program performing MPI I/O to single file (Using MPI 2.0). <br>



<!-- ************download start here ***************--> 

     ( Download source code : 
   <a href ="../ioperf-threads-codes/mpi-io-write-single-file.c"> 
         <I> <FONT COLOR = "blue"> mpi-io-write-single-file.c</FONT></I> </a>) <BR> <BR>

  </span> </p> 

    
<!-- ************Download Ends  here ***************--> 
 </td>
 </tr> 


<!-- ******************** Title for Example 1.4 ends ******************* -->

</tbody>
